00:18:01,982 --> 00:18:04,384
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
ABOUT TWO HOURS FROM
THE CITY OF AKIHABARA

375
00:18:04,484 --> 00:18:06,587
ON HORSEBACK AND COVERED
WAGON OR CAISSON,

376
00:18:06,687 --> 00:18:09,455
WHERE SOUTHERN TOKYO WOULD
BE IN THE REAL WORLD,

