00:18:43,356 --> 00:18:46,793
(ORCHESTRAL MUSIC PLAYING)

382
00:18:51,197 --> 00:18:53,066
(SHEEN)

383
00:18:53,166 --> 00:18:54,300
[MICHITAKA]
THIS IS, UH, PRETTY.

384
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,036
