00:18:56,136 --> 00:18:59,405
[KRUSTY]
JUST THINK OF EVERYONE AS A
BRIER WEASEL, THAT MIGHT HELP.

386
00:18:59,506 --> 00:19:03,409
[MISA] I DON'T THINK
THAT PROCESS WORKS
FOR EVERYONE, MY LORD.

387
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:05,145
[AKATSUKI]
I REALLY LOOK AWKWARD.
