GOBBLE YOU UP...

394
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,461
MY LITTLE BLUEBERRY.

395
00:19:21,562 --> 00:19:23,530
[SHIROE, THINKING]
OH, MY GOD, I WAS RIGHT.

396
00:19:23,630 --> 00:19:26,366
SHE'S ONLY HERE
BECAUSE OF AKATSUKI.

397
00:19:26,466 --> 00:19:28,935
[AKATSUKI] I JUST WANT
OUT OF THIS THING.

398
00:19:29,035 --> 00:19:30,370
I DON'T DO DRESSES.

399
00:19:30,470 --> 00:19:33,239
