CONCEAL MY WEAPONS.

400
00:19:33,339 --> 00:19:34,641
(HENRIETTA GASPS)

401
00:19:34,741 --> 00:19:37,143
WHOA. WHERE ON
EARTH WERE YOU
KEEPING THAT THING?

402
00:19:37,243 --> 00:19:38,278
(MICHITAKA CHUCKLES)

403
00:19:38,378 --> 00:19:39,546
[AKATSUKI] MY LORD!
[SHIROE] UH...

404
00:19:39,646 --> 00:19:41,347
[KRUSTY] I GOT TO HAND
IT TO YOU, SHIROE.

405
00:19:41,447 --> 00:19:43,416
YOUR COMPOSURE IS
INSPIRING US ALL.

406
00:19:43,517 --> 00:19:45,852
BIG POLITICAL MASTERMIND
LIKE YOU? COME ON.

