00:19:56,262 --> 00:19:59,365
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS.

412
00:19:59,465 --> 00:20:01,367
[SERJIAD] THANK YOU
FOR JOINING US TONIGHT.

413
00:20:01,467 --> 00:20:03,036
(ROUND TABLE GASPS)

414
00:20:03,136 --> 00:20:05,171
I AM DUKE SERJIAD COWEN.

415
00:20:05,271 --> 00:20:06,873
AS THE DUKE OF MAIHAMA,

416
00:20:06,973 --> 00:20:10,944
I AM THE RULER OF THE
CAPITAL OF EASTAL'S LEAGUE
OF FREEDOM CITIES.

417
00:20:11,044 --> 00:20:14,380
[SHIROE, THINKING]
OH, WOW. HE'S A REAL NOBLEMAN.

418
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:18,318
[KRUSTY] YOU GRACE,
THANK YOU FOR INVITING US.

419
00:20:18,418 --> 00:20:24,157
I AM KRUSTY, THE REPRESENTATIVE
FOR AKIHABARA'S ROUND
TABLE CONFERENCE.

420
00:20:24,257 --> 00:20:26,259
[SHIROE, THINKING]
THAT WAS GUTSY.

421
00:20:26,359 --> 00:20:29,329
KRUSTY EVEN LOOKS LIKE
A NOBLEMAN HIMSELF.

422
00:20:29,429 --> 00:20:32,265
[SHIROE] OH! AND I
AM SHIROE, YOUR GRACE.

423
00:20:32,365 --> 00:20:34,901
IT'S INDEED A
PLEASURE TO MEET YOU.

424
00:20:35,001 --> 00:20:39,239
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
SERJIAD COWEN, LORD OF
THE LARGEST EASTERN CITY,

425
00:20:39,339 --> 00:20:41,174
THE CAPITAL CITY
OF MAIHAMA,

426
00:20:41,274 --> 00:20:46,479
EASILY THE MOST POWERFUL
PERSON IN EASTAL, LEAGUE
OF FREEDOM CITIES.

427
00:20:48,014 --> 00:20:49,449
[SERJIAD] I SEE.

428
00:20:49,550 --> 00:20:51,718
SO YOUR GUILDS ARE
LIKE NOBILITY,

429
00:20:51,818 --> 00:20:54,688
BUT WITHOUT LAND OF
THEIR OWN TO RULE OVER.

430
00:20:54,788 --> 00:20:59,492
AND I TAKE IT THE GUILDS
GUIDE POLICY THROUGH
DISCUSSION AND DEBATE.

431
00:20:59,593 --> 00:21:03,196
THE STRUCTURE SEEMS COMPARABLE
TO THE WAY WE RUN EASTAL...

432
00:21:03,296 --> 00:21:05,098
ON A SMALLER SCALE, OF COURSE.

433
00:21:05,198 --> 00:21:06,967
[KRUSTY] CORRECT, YOUR GRACE.

434
00:21:07,067 --> 00:21:09,836
[SERJIAD] WELL, THEN,
I'M ALREADY SEEING A PROBLEM
WITH OUR INITIAL OVERTURE

435
00:21:09,936 --> 00:21:14,340
OF GRANTING A NOBLE TITLE
TO ONLY ONE GUILD MASTER,

436
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:16,209
IT WOULD CAUSE
NEEDLESS FRICTION.

437
00:21:16,309 --> 00:21:17,844
[HENRIETTA]
OK, SHIROE.

438
00:21:17,944 --> 00:21:21,615
AS EXPECTED, WE'RE ATTRACTING
A LOT OF ATTENTION TO OURSELVES.

439
00:21:21,715 --> 00:21:24,450
WE'RE GETTING ATTENTION,
BUT NO ONE'S TALKING TO US.

440
00:21:24,551 --> 00:21:27,287
[HENRIETTA] OUT OF
RESPECT FOR SERJIAD?
[SHIROE] NO.

441
00:21:27,387 --> 00:21:30,190
[SHIROE, THINKING]
MORE THAN LIKELY, WE'RE GETTING
THE EXCLUSIVE EAR OF THE DUKE

442
00:21:30,290 --> 00:21:33,493
BECAUSE INASMUCH AS
WE'RE CURIOUS ABOUT
THE PEOPLE OF THE LAND,

443
00:21:33,594 --> 00:21:37,263
THEY ARE EQUALLY AS CURIOUS
AND APPREHENSIVE ABOUT US.

444
00:21:37,363 --> 00:21:40,033
THEY'RE NERVOUS, VERY NERVOUS.

445
00:21:40,133 --> 00:21:42,402
THEY'RE PLAYING THE SAME
GAME WE ARE, ESSENTIALLY:

446
00:21:42,503 --> 00:21:44,070
VERBAL FENCING,
ENGAGE US IN CONVERSATION

447
00:21:44,170 --> 00:21:48,041
WITHOUT REVEALING TOO MUCH
ABOUT THEMSELVES IN THE PROCESS.

448
00:21:48,141 --> 00:21:49,743
DODGE, WEAVE, PARRY.

449
00:21:49,843 --> 00:21:52,378
THIS IS GONNA BE
A TOUGH NUT TO CRACK.

450
00:21:55,148 --> 00:21:57,117
(MURMURING)

451
00:21:57,217 --> 00:22:00,386
[MICHITAKA] WHOA.
[KAYU] HEY, I'VE NEVER SEEN
A REAL PRINCESS BEFORE.

452
00:22:00,486 --> 00:22:04,725
[SERJIAD] THAT'S MY
GRANDDAUGHTER IN THE CENTER
WEARING THE LAVENDER.

453
00:22:04,825 --> 00:22:07,093
[MICHITAKA]
AND SHE'S GORGEOUS.

454
00:22:07,193 --> 00:22:08,662
[KRUSTY]
WHAT'S HER NAME?

455
00:22:08,762 --> 00:22:12,065
[SERJIAD]
HMM. RAYNESHIA.

456
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,636
(BUGS CHIRPING)

457
00:22:15,736 --> 00:22:17,638
[NAOTSUGU] AND TOMORROW
FOR GROUP TRAINING,

458
00:22:17,738 --> 00:22:21,742
YOU'RE ACTUALLY GOING TO GO
INSIDE THE DUNGEON ITSELF.

459
00:22:21,842 --> 00:22:23,710
[TOYA AND RUNDELLHAUS]
DUNGEON!

460
00:22:23,810 --> 00:22:27,147
[NYAN‐TA] THIS PARTICULAR
DUNGEON IS CALLED
THE FOREST OF LAGLANDA.

461
00:22:27,247 --> 00:22:30,483
[TOYA] ALL RIGHT!
[RUNDELLHAUS] YOU GUYS
ARE IN FOR A REAL TREAT.

462
00:22:30,584 --> 00:22:31,752
[NAOTSUGU] BY THE WAY,

463
00:22:31,852 --> 00:22:33,754
YOU'RE GONNA BE GOING IN
THERE WITHOUT US.

464
00:22:33,854 --> 00:22:35,756
[TOYA] HUH?
(RUNDELLHAUS CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)

465
00:22:35,856 --> 00:22:38,725
[TOYA]
WITHOUT TRAINERS?
REALLY?

466
00:22:38,825 --> 00:22:40,894
OH, SHIROE...

467
00:24:15,021 --> 00:24:18,291
[AKATSUKI, VOICE‐OVER]
A BOUNTIFUL BANQUET CAN ALSO
BE A PLACE OF POLITICS

468
00:24:18,391 --> 00:24:20,060
WHERE OPPOSING
GROUPS COLLIDE.

469
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:23,096
THE NOBLES TRY TO GAIN
CONTROL OF THE ADVENTURERS,

470
00:24:23,196 --> 00:24:26,266
WHILE SHIROE AND
THE ROUND TABLE ARE
FORCED TO NEGOTIATE.

471
00:24:26,366 --> 00:24:32,238
MEANWHILE, MINORI, TOYA,
AND THEIR COMPANIONS
FACE A HARSH REALITY.

472
00:24:32,338 --> 00:24:35,108
[SHIROE] ALWAYS LOOK
30 SECONDS AHEAD.

